&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/MIAMI-WALL-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8398&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/MIAMI-WALL-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MIAMI- WALL- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;285&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;WALL Lounge is located at the W South Beach Hotel with the entrance right outside the garden.&nbsp; Its rich, dark and elegant interior is the embodiment of sophistication, luxury and style.&nbsp; Expect a young and hip South Beach crowd at this intimate and upscale nightclub.&nbsp; WALL&rsquo;s unique and open design allows for a constant flow and don&rsquo;t be surprised if you spot a celebrity or two. Dress to impress.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wallmiami.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;WALL&amp;#8217;s website&lt;/a&gt;,&nbsp;contact WALL by phone at +1-305-938-3130&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Table location and beverage minimums will be provided at the time of reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Table Reservation provides entrance without cover charge, your table is yours for the evening, arrive at any hour.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wall requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation. A deposit in the amount of&nbsp;50% of table minimum&nbsp;might&nbsp;be taken at the time of booking and will apply to the evening. Deposits are non-refundable if cancellation isn&rsquo;t made at least 24 hours prior to reservation date/time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not cancelled 24 hours prior to the reservation&nbsp;date or in the event of a no show, a fee in the amount of&nbsp;50% of your table minimum&nbsp;will be charged to your credit card.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the nightclub by phone or email 24 hours prior to your arrival date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

